' COLOR LEGEND
' ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
legend right
  | Color | Layer |
  |<#FFCC66> Gold | Data Classes (from YAML/JSON) |
  |<#80E0D0> Teal | Engine + Sessions + Resolution |
  |<#FF9933> Orange | Build Path |
  |<#B3D9FF> Light Blue | API Handlers |
  |<#CC9966> Brown | Ingestion Path |
  |<#CC99FF> Purple | Orchestration |
  |<#E6E6E6> Gray | Infrastructure + Connections |
  |<#B3FFB3> Green | Plugin System |
endlegend

@enduml
